extends ../_layout

block vars
  - var bodyClass = 'Work Koala-app'
  - var header = true

block content
  .Work__content
    section.Grid.center.Work__main
      .Cell.five
        h2.Work__title.h1.text-center.uppercase Koala App
        p.Work__description Koala is a web app built to help web developers in their job-seeking process. I worked with a team of 3 talented individuals on this full-stack MERN application (MongoDB, ExpressJS, ReactJS, and NodeJS).
    section.Grid.Work__role.center
      .Cell.six.text-center
        h2.h5 Role
        h3.Work__role-title.h4 Technical Lead &amp; UI Developer
        ul
          li Initial set-up of Express Server and configuration
          li Webpack configuration
          li Configuration and deployment to Heroku
          li Github repository manager
          li UI/UX design and development
    section.Work__UX
      .Grid.center.stretch
        //- img(src="/img/koala-bg.jpg", alt="").Work__UX-img
        .Cell.six
          .UX__content
            h2.h3.text-center User Flows &amp; Wireframes
            p I led the team in a few exercises to determine user flows. We identified key areas where on which to focus and where pain points might arise. Because of the time limit (3 week project) we were limited in our ability to do extensive user research. We conducted a couple of interviews and used those to inform Koala's workflow process. I wireframed the app, used those to quick user testing, and proceeded to design and development.
    section.Work__screens
      .Grid.center
        .Cell.eight
          h3.text-center Staying Organized is Key
          p Koala provides a way to not only find jobs but a way to manage the details throughout your process. Koalaâ€™s built-in job search engine takes the hassle out of going to different sites to search for jobs. Browsing the latest job posting from the largest career sites could not be easier. You can add and remove an unlimited number of jobs to your system and manage them any way you want.
      .Grid.center
        .Cell.eight
          img(src="/img/work/koala-imac.png", alt="Koala App on iMac")
      .Grid.middle
        .Cell.six
          h3 Keeping Notes
          p Notes are designed to help you keep track of the jobs in your system. Want a note to remind you what day you applied for this job, who you spoke to on your phone interview, what you need to study before your in-person interview? Koala is here to help.
        .Cell.six
          img(src="/img/work/koala-macbook.png", alt="Koala App on laptop")
